1026.name: Ventus-Press

1027.desc: Reduces Movement SPD by <color=#fb8037>25%</color> for <color=#fb8037>&Param2&</color>s, up to <color=#fb8037>&Param3&</color> stacks.At <color=#fb8037>&Param3&</color> stacks, it converts into Freeze for <color=#fb8037>&Param4&</color>s.

1029.name: Melt Armor
1029.desc: Increase target DMG received by 40% for 5s

1030.desc: Each Electric Soul increases the Trekker's damage by 5%. When reaching 3 Electric Souls, Electric Soul will be activated and will automatically seek out enemies, dealing area of effect Lux DMG

1031.name: Unstable Flowery Cloud
1031.desc:
Determined after throwing Unstable Flowery Cloud:
Normal: Explode 1 time
Success: Explode 2 times
Great Success: Explode 3 times

1032.name: Ring of Fog
1032.desc:
Summon Dew to accumulate Ring of Fog
For every 3 Dew summons, expand 1 stack of Ring of Fog, up to 3 stacks
Deal 30% ATK as Aqua DMG to targets within Ring of Fog every 2s
If less than 3 Dews are casted within 10s, remove 1 stack of Ring of Fog

1033.name: Wind Realm
1033.desc:
Firing Wind Shots can accumulate 15 Ventus Energy
Accumulate 60 Ventus Energy to expand 1 stack of Wind Zone, up to 3 stacks
Each stack of Wind Zone increases Ventus DMG received by the target by 5%
If less than 3 Wind Shots are fired within 10s, remove 1 stack of Wind Zone

1040.name: Light Explosion

1042.name: Mark of Great Kamaitachi

1049.name: Dr. Cloud
1049.desc: In this state, increase Trekker ATK and all Unstable Flowery Cloud the Trekker throws is guaranteed to be Great Success

1050.name: Flowery Cloud
1050.desc: Includes Unstable Flowery Cloud and Stable Flowery Cloud

1051.name: Runic Ice
1051.desc: Each Runic Ice increases Trekker Aqua DMG and weakens target hit with Dew, reducing the target's damage

1052.name: Heart
